		<div class="content">
		<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000;"><strong><br /><br /><span style="font-size: xx-large;">《这山唱那山》音乐会</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br /></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: large;">时间：2012年9月30日                 地点：国家大剧院音乐厅 <span style="color: #000000;"><br /></span><span style="color: #000000;">   </span></span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><br /><span style="font-size: large;">指挥：阎伯政（国家一级指挥）   钢琴伴奏：全艳 王燕           主持：张思路 <span style="color: #000000;"><br /></span><span style="color: #000000;">   <br /></span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size: large;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">演唱：中央民族乐团民歌合唱队   演奏：中央民族乐团喜洋洋室内乐队<br /><br /></span></strong><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span> 
<p><strong> </strong></p>
</p>
 
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"> </p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">一、合唱《老北京》                                    根据老北京市声 亚雄改词 伯政编合唱</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">              《卓玛拉》                                                                            真知词 秋加措曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">              《瞧情郎》                                                        根据东北民歌改编 李民编配</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                                                          领唱：杨丹妮</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;"><br />         二、琵琶独奏《彝族舞曲》                                                                  王惠然编曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                                                           演奏：蒋彦</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">三、男声无伴奏合唱《澧水船夫号子》                              根据湖南民歌 营震编曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">          领唱：张平（国家一级演员） 张向华（文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">四、二胡齐奏《战马奔腾》                                                                            陈耀星曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                                           演奏：李福华（国家一级演员）等</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">五、男女声对唱《一朵鲜花鲜又鲜》                         葛炎 刘琼词 罗宗贤 葛炎曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                                                                  演唱：尤龙    唐文娟</span></p>
</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;"><br />           六、新疆组曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">              1、民歌联唱                                      王洛宾根据新疆民歌改编 王丹红编配</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">             《阿拉木汗》                                                                               维吾尔族民歌</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                 演唱：刘扬（文化部文华奖获奖者、文化部首届中国歌剧节获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">            《可爱的一朵玫瑰花》                                          哈萨克族民歌 丁善德改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                               演唱：贾静思（第六届东方旋律国际音乐节获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">              2、小合奏《美丽的新疆》                                                               刘明源曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                             新疆木碗唢呐领奏：陈力宝       打击乐领奏：李文博</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">
