<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">        七、无伴奏合唱《包楞调》                                  根据山东民歌改编 方兵编曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                           《毛风细雨》                                       根据贵州民歌改编 方兵编曲</span></p>
