<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">         八、女声独唱《人说山西好风光》                                        乔羽词 张棣昌曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                        《玛依拉变奏曲》                            新疆哈萨克族民歌  胡廷江改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                   演唱：谢琳（国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
