<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">         九、男声四重唱《香巴拉并不遥远》                                    黄志龙词 边洛曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                           《回娘家》                                                       河北民歌 李文平编配</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                                        演唱：张向华    肖笑    刘松焘    赵健</span></p>
