<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                   《新编喜洋洋——幸福年》                                       刘明源曲  刘湘整编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: medium;">                                         板胡领奏：刘湘（国家一级演员） </span></p>
